>>>>>>> Footcare networks are usually made up of people with diabetes,
healthcare professionals and commissioners. They come together to improve the
quality of footcare services for people with diabetes across primary,
>>>>>>> Diabetes Footcare Networks were well established across England but
lost funding for the coordinators after the closure of NHS-Diabetes. Some
networks have continued or are re-forming but coverage is patchy. We have
listed the details for the networks we are aware of across England.
